Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:43.69,OP_CH,NTP,440,0,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}カルマ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:49.91,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}白金で断つ運命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:49.91,OP_CH,NTP,0,200,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}ひかり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:49.91,OP_CH,NTP,200,0,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}さだめ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:53.72,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}Stand up! Stand up! Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.96,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}打ち込むのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:02:59.58,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}All right now All right now All right now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:03.07,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}誇りのBullet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:05.37,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}Break you down Break you down Break you down
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:14.26,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}拳放つ 聖なるヴィジョン Stand Proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.81,0:02:20.50,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}百年沉睡的甦醒在召喚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:27.06,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}星塵遙呼 相繼匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:31.93,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}男子漢一行已啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:37.56,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}踏上穿越時間的沙漠之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:43.69,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}宿命 如同一串錯綜連橫的枷鎖
